fields.name: Beige Outdoor Training Shoes
fields.description: Lightweight beige outdoor training shoes with breathable cutout design. Features durable rubber outsole and elastic lacing system for easy wear and comfort during workouts or outdoor activities.

fields.name: Waterproof Smartphone Case
fields.description: Clear waterproof smartphone case with lanyard. Perfect for protecting your device during water activities, beach trips, or outdoor adventures. Features touch-sensitive material that allows full functionality while keeping your phone dry and secure.

fields.name: Red Cargo Athletic Shorts
fields.description: High-waisted red cargo athletic shorts with drawstring closure and zippered pockets. Made from breathable, lightweight material perfect for workouts, running, or casual wear. Features elastic waistband for comfortable fit.

fields.name: Colorblock Corduroy Jacket
fields.description: Trendy colorblock corduroy jacket featuring green, brown and cream panels. Oversized fit with button closure, multiple pockets and frayed hem detail. Perfect for layering over workout clothes or casual outfits in cooler weather.

fields.name: Grey Outdoor Hiking Sandals
fields.description: Durable grey hiking sandals with protective toe cap and cushioned footbed. Features quick-dry lining, adjustable straps, and rugged outsole perfect for hiking, water activities, or everyday outdoor wear. Available in size 40 and other sizes.

fields.name: Army Green Fleece Vest
fields.description: Cozy army green fleece vest with high collar and full zipper closure. Features hand pockets and sleeveless design perfect for layering over long-sleeve tops. Ideal for outdoor activities, casual wear, or as an additional layer for warmth.

fields.name: Black & Pink Hiking Boots
fields.description: Durable black hiking boots with pink accents. Features high-top ankle support, rugged tread pattern, water-resistant materials, and cushioned insole. Perfect for trail hiking, outdoor adventures, and all-terrain walking.

fields.name: Olive Green Hiking Shoes
fields.description: Military green outdoor hiking shoes with 'SPORT' branding and durable lace-up design. Features padded collar, grippy rubber outsole, and water-resistant exterior. Perfect for trail walking, outdoor activities, and casual wear.

fields.name: Multi-Color Workout Headbands Set
fields.description: Set of 7 wide athletic headbands in various colors and patterns. Made of stretchy, moisture-wicking fabric perfect for keeping hair back during workouts. Available in blue, green, multicolor, red, black, and pink variations. Comfortable fit for all-day wear.

fields.name: Mint Green Athletic Leggings
fields.description: High-waisted mint green athletic leggings with side pocket and contoured panels. Made from stretchy, moisture-wicking fabric perfect for hiking, gym workouts, or casual wear. Features a comfortable waistband and flattering fit.

fields.name: Gray Cargo Utility Pants
fields.description: Relaxed fit gray cargo pants with multiple utility pockets and button closure. Features durable cotton material perfect for outdoor activities or urban streetwear. Can be styled high-waisted or low-rise for versatile looks.

fields.name: Black Tactical Jogger Pants
fields.description: Black cargo jogger pants with multiple utility pockets and gold accent tags. Features drawstring waist, elastic ankle cuffs, and lightweight tactical design. Perfect for urban adventures, casual wear, or stylish athleisure outfits.

fields.name: Packable Bucket Hat
fields.description: Lightweight packable bucket hat with carabiner clip for easy carrying. Available in six colors: beige, pink, olive green, gray, navy blue, and black. Features a foldable design that compresses into a compact circle when not in use. Perfect for hiking, fishing, or beach days.

fields.name: Army Green Performance Vest
fields.description: Army green fleece vest with high collar and full zipper closure. Features hand pockets and sleeveless design perfect for layering over long-sleeve tops. Ideal for outdoor activities, casual wear, or as an additional layer for warmth.
